                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200217-9-victim135 t18200217-9-viclabel51"></join>, which starts from the <placeName id="t18200217-9-crimeloc52">Four Swans' yard, Bishopsgate-street</placeName>
